name: Lets Fly Cheaper
overview:
Our goal at Lets Fly Cheaper is to provide outstanding service while getting you the lowest price for airline tickets out there. By constantly and consistently re-negotiating airline fares directly with the airlines, we are able to offer lower fares than any other available. With the use of airline consolidators and wholesalers, we offer the same exact seats as your fellow passenger, but you could save up to 30-70% than the guy sitting next to you. The benefit with working with airline consolidators is that we have access to airline tickets simply not available on airline websites or any other travel booking website. Call one of our live agents and we will give you a personalized airfare quote.

We offer cheap fares whether it’s a one way or an open jaw and we specialize in last minute tickets and multi-city flights to any destination in the world. We guarantee you quality service and a cheap airline ticket. Our agents are standing by to take your calls.
